items.title: Trump threatens to hit Apple with 25% tariff on iPhone sales
items.description: President Trump said he would impose steep tariff on Apple unless company starts manufacturing some iPhones in the U.S.

items.title: Bones found on N.J. beaches ID'd as captain of doomed 19th-century ship
items.description: The skeletal remains, including a skull, were found on a number of South Jersey beaches between 1995 and 2013.

items.title: Relatives of Venezuelan detainees in CECOT find comfort in support group
items.description: Mothers and relatives of the Venezuelan detainees in CECOT have been communicating about their loved ones in a WhatsApp group.

items.title: Junior ROTC cadet killed in Parkland shooting is honorary West Point 2025 grad
items.description: Peter Wang, honored as a member of the 2025 West Point class, was just 15 when he was killed in the 2018 mass shooting in Parkland, Florida.
